[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":830},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F12\u002F06\u002Fbuy-a-domain-for-your-blog-with-github-pages-and-cloudflare\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F12\u002F06\u002Fbuy-a-domain-for-your-blog-with-github-pages-and-cloudflare\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F12\u002F06\u002Fbuy-a-domain-for-your-blog-with-github-pages-and-cloudflare\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F12\u002F06\u002Fbuy-a-domain-for-your-blog-with-github-pages-and-cloudflare\u002F":806,"related:\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F12\u002F06\u002Fbuy-a-domain-for-your-blog-with-github-pages-and-cloudflare\u002F":815},"\u002Fother\u002F20221206\u002F2011045213\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":786,"date":787,"description":788,"extension":789,"lang":790,"meta":791,"navigation":792,"path":793,"readingMinutes":794,"seo":795,"standalone":796,"stem":797,"tags":798,"tldr":802,"updated":803,"url":804,"__hash__":805},"content\u002Fen\u002FMisc\u002Fbuy-a-domain-for-your-blog-with-github-pages-and-cloudflare.md","Buy a Domain (Google Domains) and Point It at Your Blog on GitHub Pages With Cloudflare","4502130112",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":777},"minimark",[11,19,24,43,46,50,53,69,72,85,92,99,103,110,117,131,134,154,157,161,164,174,210,217,221,235,245,252,487,490,496,499,509,512,518,525,536,539,551,555,558,581,584,593,599,602,605,611,614,620,623,629,632,638,651,658,664,667,682,685,688,694,697,703,706,712,715,718,724,727,733,736,742,745,749,752,758,764,770,773],[12,13,14],"p",{},[15,16],"img",{"alt":17,"src":18},"Google Domains","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FgdGyaRl.png",[20,21,23],"h2",{"id":22},"intro","Intro",[25,26,27,40],"blockquote",{},[12,28,29,33,34,39],{},[30,31,32],"strong",{},"Note","\nThis post is historical reference. Google Domains was discontinued in 2023 and transferred to Squarespace. For new domain purchases today, check out my newer post: ",[35,36,38],"a",{"href":37},"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2026\u002F02\u002F15\u002Fgoogle-domains-shutdown-cloudflare-domain-tutorial\u002F","Google Domains Shutdown: Set Up Your Cloudflare Domain Step by Step",".",[12,41,42],{},"The GitHub Pages + Cloudflare setup portion below is still applicable if you already have a domain (whether from Google Domains, Squarespace, Cloudflare, or elsewhere).",[12,44,45],{},"Plenty of people host their tech blogs on GitHub Pages or GitLab Pages and want a custom URL for it. This post walks through buying a domain (originally on Google Domains), pointing it at GitHub Pages, and putting Cloudflare in front for free SSL\u002Facceleration.",[20,47,49],{"id":48},"why-bother-with-a-custom-domain","Why bother with a custom domain?",[12,51,52],{},"Let me start with why you'd pay for a domain when GitHub gives you a free URL.",[12,54,55,56,60,61,64,65,68],{},"GitHub Pages and GitLab Pages give you a URL based on your username — if your GitHub handle is ",[57,58,59],"code",{},"israynotarray",", you get ",[57,62,63],{},"israynotarray.github.io",". GitLab equivalent: ",[57,66,67],{},"israynotarray.gitlab.io",". That's the default URL for your blog or project portfolio.",[12,70,71],{},"What's bad about that? A few things:",[73,74,75,79,82],"ul",{},[76,77,78],"li",{},"If the host has an outage, your site dies — your URL points at their infrastructure",[76,80,81],{},"If the host kills the feature, you lose your SEO equity",[76,83,84],{},"The URL isn't memorable, and it's tied to your platform identity",[12,86,87,88,91],{},"The worst case is ",[30,89,90],{},"migrating your blog",". If you move to your own hosting later, your SEO juice doesn't follow — anyone who linked to your old URL is broken. Free URLs are fine for project portfolios and quick projects, but for a long-term blog, get a domain.",[12,93,94,95,39],{},"If you want a primer on domains in general, see my earlier ",[35,96,98],{"href":97},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20201005\u002F1370103497\u002F","What's a domain? (article in Mandarin)",[20,100,102],{"id":101},"google-domains-historical","Google Domains (historical)",[25,104,105],{},[12,106,107,109],{},[30,108,32],{},"\nGoogle Domains was discontinued in 2023. The screenshots and walkthrough below are historical. For new purchases, use one of the active registrars (Cloudflare Registrar, Namecheap, Squarespace, etc.) — the setup steps for pointing the domain at GitHub Pages are similar regardless of registrar.",[12,111,112,113,116],{},"Original signup flow — open ",[57,114,115],{},"https:\u002F\u002Fdomains.google.com\u002Fregistrar\u002Fsearch",", type the domain you want, and Google would show availability and pricing.",[12,118,119,120,123,124,123,127,130],{},"Each TLD (",[57,121,122],{},".com",", ",[57,125,126],{},".tw",[57,128,129],{},".dev",") has different pricing. Pick a TLD and a name that's memorable. Once you'd chosen one, you'd add it to cart.",[12,132,133],{},"In the cart you'd configure:",[73,135,136,142,148],{},[76,137,138,141],{},[30,139,140],{},"Registration period"," — typically 1-10 years",[76,143,144,147],{},[30,145,146],{},"Privacy protection"," — hides your registrant info from WHOIS lookups. Strongly recommended. Free on Google Domains, sometimes paid elsewhere.",[76,149,150,153],{},[30,151,152],{},"Auto-renew"," — automatic renewal before expiration. Recommended for long-term sites.",[12,155,156],{},"After checkout, the domain was registered to your Google account.",[20,158,160],{"id":159},"setting-up-dns-for-github-pages","Setting up DNS for GitHub Pages",[12,162,163],{},"This is the part that's still applicable regardless of where you bought the domain.",[12,165,166,167,173],{},"We need to point the domain at GitHub Pages. GitHub Pages' IPs (from the ",[35,168,172],{"href":169,"rel":170},"https:\u002F\u002Fdocs.github.com\u002Fen\u002Fpages\u002Fconfiguring-a-custom-domain-for-your-github-pages-site\u002Fmanaging-a-custom-domain-for-your-github-pages-site",[171],"nofollow","official docs","):",[175,176,181],"pre",{"className":177,"code":178,"language":179,"meta":180,"style":180},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","185.199.108.153\n185.199.109.153\n185.199.110.153\n185.199.111.153\n","bash","",[57,182,183,192,198,204],{"__ignoreMap":180},[184,185,188],"span",{"class":186,"line":187},"line",1,[184,189,191],{"class":190},"s_sBn","185.199.108.153\n",[184,193,195],{"class":186,"line":194},2,[184,196,197],{"class":190},"185.199.109.153\n",[184,199,201],{"class":186,"line":200},3,[184,202,203],{"class":190},"185.199.110.153\n",[184,205,207],{"class":186,"line":206},4,[184,208,209],{"class":190},"185.199.111.153\n",[12,211,212,213,216],{},"At your registrar's DNS settings, add an ",[30,214,215],{},"A record"," for each of these IPs (no host name \u002F @ root).",[20,218,220],{"id":219},"configure-github-pages","Configure GitHub Pages",[12,222,223,224,227,228,231,232,39],{},"Open the Repository for your GitHub Pages site. This needs to be your ",[30,225,226],{},"user-level repo"," — the one named ",[57,229,230],{},"yourusername.github.io",". For me that's ",[57,233,234],{},"hsiangfeng.github.io",[12,236,237,238,241,242,39],{},"For the example I'm using a fresh test account ",[57,239,240],{},"share-jack",", so I create a repo named ",[57,243,244],{},"share-jack.github.io",[12,246,247,248,251],{},"I uploaded a simple ",[57,249,250],{},"index.html",":",[175,253,257],{"className":254,"code":255,"language":256,"meta":180,"style":180},"language-html shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","\u003C!DOCTYPE html>\n\u003Chtml lang=\"en\">\n\u003Chead>\n  \u003Cmeta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  \u003Cmeta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n  \u003Cmeta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  \u003Ctitle>Google Domain + GitHub Pages demo\u003C\u002Ftitle>\n\u003C\u002Fhead>\n\u003Cbody>\n  \u003Ch1>This is a Google Domain + GitHub Pages demo site\u003C\u002Fh1>\n  \u003Cp>\n    Full tutorial:\n    \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fother\u002F20221206\u002F2011045213\u002F\">Buy a Domain and Set Up Your Blog URL\u003C\u002Fa>\n  \u003C\u002Fp>\n\u003C\u002Fbody>\n\u003C\u002Fhtml>\n","html",[57,258,259,276,295,304,322,347,371,386,396,406,421,430,436,459,469,478],{"__ignoreMap":180},[184,260,261,265,269,273],{"class":186,"line":187},[184,262,264],{"class":263},"sMAXC","\u003C!",[184,266,268],{"class":267},"sKpQp","DOCTYPE",[184,270,272],{"class":271},"sCcAr"," html",[184,274,275],{"class":263},">\n",[184,277,278,281,283,286,289,293],{"class":186,"line":194},[184,279,280],{"class":263},"\u003C",[184,282,256],{"class":267},[184,284,285],{"class":271}," lang",[184,287,288],{"class":263},"=",[184,290,292],{"class":291},"sTRMh","\"en\"",[184,294,275],{"class":263},[184,296,297,299,302],{"class":186,"line":200},[184,298,280],{"class":263},[184,300,301],{"class":267},"head",[184,303,275],{"class":263},[184,305,306,309,312,315,317,320],{"class":186,"line":206},[184,307,308],{"class":263},"  \u003C",[184,310,311],{"class":267},"meta",[184,313,314],{"class":271}," charset",[184,316,288],{"class":263},[184,318,319],{"class":291},"\"UTF-8\"",[184,321,275],{"class":263},[184,323,325,327,329,332,334,337,340,342,345],{"class":186,"line":324},5,[184,326,308],{"class":263},[184,328,311],{"class":267},[184,330,331],{"class":271}," http-equiv",[184,333,288],{"class":263},[184,335,336],{"class":291},"\"X-UA-Compatible\"",[184,338,339],{"class":271}," content",[184,341,288],{"class":263},[184,343,344],{"class":291},"\"IE=edge\"",[184,346,275],{"class":263},[184,348,350,352,354,357,359,362,364,366,369],{"class":186,"line":349},6,[184,351,308],{"class":263},[184,353,311],{"class":267},[184,355,356],{"class":271}," name",[184,358,288],{"class":263},[184,360,361],{"class":291},"\"viewport\"",[184,363,339],{"class":271},[184,365,288],{"class":263},[184,367,368],{"class":291},"\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"",[184,370,275],{"class":263},[184,372,374,376,379,382,384],{"class":186,"line":373},7,[184,375,308],{"class":263},[184,377,378],{"class":267},"title",[184,380,381],{"class":263},">Google Domain + GitHub Pages demo\u003C\u002F",[184,383,378],{"class":267},[184,385,275],{"class":263},[184,387,389,392,394],{"class":186,"line":388},8,[184,390,391],{"class":263},"\u003C\u002F",[184,393,301],{"class":267},[184,395,275],{"class":263},[184,397,399,401,404],{"class":186,"line":398},9,[184,400,280],{"class":263},[184,402,403],{"class":267},"body",[184,405,275],{"class":263},[184,407,409,411,414,417,419],{"class":186,"line":408},10,[184,410,308],{"class":263},[184,412,413],{"class":267},"h1",[184,415,416],{"class":263},">This is a Google Domain + GitHub Pages demo site\u003C\u002F",[184,418,413],{"class":267},[184,420,275],{"class":263},[184,422,424,426,428],{"class":186,"line":423},11,[184,425,308],{"class":263},[184,427,12],{"class":267},[184,429,275],{"class":263},[184,431,433],{"class":186,"line":432},12,[184,434,435],{"class":263},"    Full tutorial:\n",[184,437,439,442,444,447,449,452,455,457],{"class":186,"line":438},13,[184,440,441],{"class":263},"    \u003C",[184,443,35],{"class":267},[184,445,446],{"class":271}," href",[184,448,288],{"class":263},[184,450,451],{"class":291},"\"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fother\u002F20221206\u002F2011045213\u002F\"",[184,453,454],{"class":263},">Buy a Domain and Set Up Your Blog URL\u003C\u002F",[184,456,35],{"class":267},[184,458,275],{"class":263},[184,460,462,465,467],{"class":186,"line":461},14,[184,463,464],{"class":263},"  \u003C\u002F",[184,466,12],{"class":267},[184,468,275],{"class":263},[184,470,472,474,476],{"class":186,"line":471},15,[184,473,391],{"class":263},[184,475,403],{"class":267},[184,477,275],{"class":263},[184,479,481,483,485],{"class":186,"line":480},16,[184,482,391],{"class":263},[184,484,256],{"class":267},[184,486,275],{"class":263},[12,488,489],{},"In the repo's Settings → Pages → \"Custom domain\" — enter your purchased domain and click Save:",[12,491,492],{},[15,493],{"alt":494,"src":495},"Custom domain","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-domain\u002Fsetting-domain.jpg",[12,497,498],{},"You'll probably see this error first:",[25,500,501],{},[12,502,503,508],{},[35,504,507],{"href":505,"rel":506},"http:\u002F\u002Fwww.israynotarray.dev",[171],"www.israynotarray.dev"," is improperly configured\nDomain's DNS record could not be retrieved. For more information, see documentation (InvalidDNSError).",[12,510,511],{},"Ignore it — give it a few minutes and the domain will start resolving:",[12,513,514],{},[15,515],{"alt":516,"src":517},"Custom domain working","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-domain\u002Fsetting-domain-2.jpg",[12,519,520,521,524],{},"You'll also see GitHub auto-added a ",[57,522,523],{},"CNAME"," file to your repo:",[175,526,530],{"className":527,"code":528,"language":529,"meta":180,"style":180},"language-txt shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","israynotarray.dev\n","txt",[57,531,532],{"__ignoreMap":180},[184,533,534],{"class":186,"line":187},[184,535,528],{},[12,537,538],{},"That file tells GitHub Pages your custom domain. GitHub Pages also issues a free SSL cert automatically.",[25,540,541],{},[12,542,543,546,547,550],{},[30,544,545],{},"Warning","\nOnce you switch GitHub Pages' Custom domain to your custom URL, all your links should use the new domain. Anyone visiting the old ",[57,548,549],{},".github.io"," URL gets auto-redirected to the new one with a 301 (so SEO is preserved).",[20,552,554],{"id":553},"bonus-adding-cloudflare","Bonus: Adding Cloudflare",[12,556,557],{},"GitHub Pages already gives you free SSL — so why add Cloudflare? Because Cloudflare adds free:",[73,559,560,563,566,569,572,575,578],{},[76,561,562],{},"Site acceleration (CDN)",[76,564,565],{},"DDoS protection",[76,567,568],{},"Site monitoring",[76,570,571],{},"Web Application Firewall (WAF)",[76,573,574],{},"Caching",[76,576,577],{},"Compression",[76,579,580],{},"Analytics",[12,582,583],{},"…all on the free tier. Optional but worth it for any production site.",[12,585,586,587,592],{},"Head to ",[35,588,591],{"href":589,"rel":590},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.cloudflare.com\u002F",[171],"Cloudflare"," and register. After login, you'll see this — click \"Add a Site\":",[12,594,595],{},[15,596],{"alt":597,"src":598},"Add a Site","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-domain\u002Fclf-1.jpg",[12,600,601],{},"(Cloudflare has localized UIs — switch language in account settings if you prefer.)",[12,603,604],{},"Enter your domain:",[12,606,607],{},[15,608],{"alt":609,"src":610},"Add domain","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-domain\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-12-06%2017.50.25.png",[12,612,613],{},"You'll land on the plan picker. Scroll down to find \"Free\":",[12,615,616],{},[15,617],{"alt":618,"src":619},"Free plan","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-domain\u002Fclf-2.jpg",[12,621,622],{},"Free plan covers a lot of features already:",[12,624,625],{},[15,626],{"alt":627,"src":628},"Free plan features","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-domain\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-12-06%2017.52.29.png",[12,630,631],{},"Now we need to switch the domain's DNS over to Cloudflare so they can handle SSL and the other features. Add a DNS record — match the screenshot:",[12,633,634],{},[15,635],{"alt":636,"src":637},"Add DNS record","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-domain\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-12-06%2017.58.05.png",[12,639,640,641,643,644,647,648,650],{},"Important — the ",[57,642,523],{}," should be named ",[57,645,646],{},"www"," and the target should be your original GitHub Pages URL (e.g., ",[57,649,244],{},").",[12,652,653,654,657],{},"Cloudflare will give you two ",[30,655,656],{},"nameservers"," to point your domain at:",[12,659,660],{},[15,661],{"alt":662,"src":663},"Nameservers","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-domain\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-12-06%2018.00.13.png",[12,665,666],{},"Example values:",[175,668,670],{"className":527,"code":669,"language":529,"meta":180,"style":180},"jillian.ns.cloudflare.com\nkaiser.ns.cloudflare.com\n",[57,671,672,677],{"__ignoreMap":180},[184,673,674],{"class":186,"line":187},[184,675,676],{},"jillian.ns.cloudflare.com\n",[184,678,679],{"class":186,"line":194},[184,680,681],{},"kaiser.ns.cloudflare.com\n",[12,683,684],{},"Save these — you'll need them next.",[12,686,687],{},"Back at your registrar (was Google Domains, now wherever your domain lives), find DNS settings → \"Custom nameservers\":",[12,689,690],{},[15,691],{"alt":692,"src":693},"Custom nameservers","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-domain\u002Fdns-clf-1.jpg",[12,695,696],{},"Enter the two Cloudflare nameservers and save:",[12,698,699],{},[15,700],{"alt":701,"src":702},"Save nameservers","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-domain\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-12-06%2018.03.27.png",[12,704,705],{},"Click \"Switch to these settings\" to actually apply:",[12,707,708],{},[15,709],{"alt":710,"src":711},"Switch","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-domain\u002Fdns-clf-2.jpg",[12,713,714],{},"If successful, you'll see \"These DNS settings are valid. Changes will publish immediately but may take some time to take effect\", and the heading changes to \"Custom nameservers (in use)\".",[12,716,717],{},"Back at Cloudflare, click \"Done, check nameservers\":",[12,719,720],{},[15,721],{"alt":722,"src":723},"Check nameservers","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-domain\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-12-06%2018.04.13.png",[12,725,726],{},"Cloudflare will verify your nameservers — takes a bit. You'll get an email confirming activation:",[12,728,729],{},[15,730],{"alt":731,"src":732},"Activation email","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-domain\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-12-06%2018.09.37.png",[12,734,735],{},"Activated in the Cloudflare dashboard:",[12,737,738],{},[15,739],{"alt":740,"src":741},"Activated","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-domain\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-12-06%2018.10.42.png",[12,743,744],{},"Everything else in Cloudflare is yours to explore — the localized UI makes it pretty discoverable.",[20,746,748],{"id":747},"cloudflare-gotcha-ssl-mode","Cloudflare gotcha — SSL mode",[12,750,751],{},"One thing that'll bite you — after setting up Cloudflare, your domain might stop working after a while. The default SSL\u002FTLS mode is \"Flexible\", which can cause this error in some browsers:",[12,753,754],{},[15,755],{"alt":756,"src":757},"SSL error","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-domain\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-12-06%2019.24.05.png",[12,759,760,761,251],{},"Fix — Cloudflare dashboard → SSL\u002FTLS → change SSL\u002FTLS mode to ",[30,762,763],{},"\"Full\"",[12,765,766],{},[15,767],{"alt":768,"src":769},"Full mode","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-domain\u002Fclf-bug.jpg",[12,771,772],{},"Now your site should work again immediately.",[774,775,776],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .s_sBn, html code.shiki .s_sBn{--shiki-default:#FFB757}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-st